WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:31.780
空に突き上げた拳の中　握り締めてる言葉
sora ni tsukiageta kobushi no naka nigirishimeteru kotoba
Her words clenched tight in a fist raised to the heavens

00:00:31.780 --> 00:00:37.100
未だ開けずに　一人見上げ願う
mada hirakezu ni hitori miage negau
The yet-unenlightened girl looks up and makes a wish

00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:45.060
流れ行く雲間の　向こう側気にして
nagareyuku kumo ma no mukou gawa kinishite
Beyond the flowing rifts between the clouds, I hear her plea

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:57.680
形のない世界を漂い歩いてる　夢　憧れ探して
katachi no nai sekai wo tadayoi aruiteru yume akogare sagashite
Wandering through this formless world, she seeks her dream

00:00:57.680 --> 00:01:04.320
まだ望みがあるとするなら
mada nozomi ga aru to suru nara
If she decides that she still desires it

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:11.440
そっと連れて行って　雲のようなその速さで
sotto tsureteitte kumo no you na sono hayasa de
I'll gently lead her there with the speed of the clouds

00:01:23.420 --> 00:01:35.960
時々誰かが　この世の中　操ってる気がして
tokidoki dareka ga kono yo no naka ayatsutteru kigashite
From time to time, she senses someone manipulating this world

00:01:35.960 --> 00:01:41.520
何とも解らず　手を合わせ祈り
nanitomo wakarazu te wo awase inori
Understanding nothing, she joins her hands in supplication

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:49.640
「自分には禍　降りかからないように」
「jibun ni wa wazawai furikakaranai you ni」
"I pray that no calamity will befall me."

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:56.460
形決まってる箱の外から　覗き込む
katachi kimatteru hako no soto kara nozokikomu
When I peer in from beyond the world of earthly form

00:01:56.460 --> 00:02:02.160
空虚（そら）見上げた　私を
sora miageta watashi wo
She sees me as she gazes up into the empty sky

00:02:02.160 --> 00:02:08.560
そんな　存在があるとするなら
sonna sonzai ga aru to suru nara
If she decides that her eyes do not deceive her

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:15.980
そっと　あぁ　連れ出して　雲のようなその強さで
sotto aa tsuredashite kumo no you na sono tsuyosa de
I'll gently carry her off with the strength of the clouds

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:53.780
あぁ　髪靡かせ　うぅ　少女は今　全て越えて行く
aa kami nabikase uu shoujo wa ima subete koeteku
Hair swaying in the wind, the girl begins the transcendence of form

00:02:53.780 --> 00:03:00.840
形のない世界を漂い歩いてる
katachi no nai sekai wo tadayoi aruiteru
Wandering through this formless world

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:06.400
 迷いない眼差しで
mayoinai manazashi de
Her gaze is now empty of doubt

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:12.960
まだ　躓くこともあるから
mada tsumazuku koto mo aru kara
But since she still falters here and there

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:20.520
そっと包み込んで　雲のようなその広さで
sotto tsutsumikonde kumo no you na sono hirosa de
I'll gently envelop her in the vastness of the clouds

